                            <comment id="12716183" author="noble.paul" created="Thu, 4 Jun 2009 08:18:23 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;this issue can be fixed in batches.  this is one low hanging fruit&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12716260" author="noble.paul" created="Thu, 4 Jun 2009 13:41:51 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;comitted revision : 781668 with &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;unlockOnStartup, useColdSearcher, maxWarmingSearchers moved to SolrConfig&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12716263" author="noble.paul" created="Thu, 4 Jun 2009 13:44:19 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;This moves the RequestHandler xml parsing to SolrConfig.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This introduces a class PluginInfo which can be used for all pluggable classes &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12716861" author="noble.paul" created="Sat, 6 Jun 2009 11:17:18 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;tested.&lt;br/&gt;
I&apos;ll commit this shortly&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
