I shall commit this shortly&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12717197" author="noble.paul" created="Mon, 8 Jun 2009 09:44:03 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;committed : r782552&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12717570" author="noble.paul" created="Tue, 9 Jun 2009 06:49:16 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;moved updateHandler, updateprocessor to solrconfig&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12717571" author="noble.paul" created="Tue, 9 Jun 2009 06:51:19 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;committed r782885&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12717613" author="noble.paul" created="Tue, 9 Jun 2009 09:36:19 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;moved searchComponent, indexReaderFactory&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12717614" author="noble.paul" created="Tue, 9 Jun 2009 09:37:54 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;committed r782913&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
